title: [Lysierian Hills, Winding Path]
description: The path winds in and out of the dense forest that surrounds you.  Normally there is a great number of small game throughout this area during the day.  At night, however, the forest falls silent, save for the occasional hoot of an owl or snarl of a lone predator.

The path winds in and out of the dense forest that surrounds you.  There is a great number of small game throughout this area.  Colorful birds perched in the trees pipe their questioning songs at you.
